00:31:00.110 --> 00:31:02.530
As you all know,
during the Korean War,

00:31:02.530 --> 00:31:06.570
US forces moved rather quickly
up through the Korean Peninsula

00:31:06.570 --> 00:31:10.160
up to the, up to the Yalu River.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:13.420
