of thousands of pages

00:31:13.420 --> 00:31:15.450
of documents were collected

00:31:15.450 --> 00:31:18.040
at various cities
all along the way.

00:31:18.040 --> 00:31:21.220
I think the bulk of what we
have was captured in the Capitol

00:31:21.220 --> 00:31:24.430
in Pyongyang, but there are
also things captured in Seoul

00:31:24.430 --> 00:31:26.200
and elsewhere along the way.

00:31:26.200 --> 00:31:31.230
The documents in this large
collection span basically the

00:31:31.230 --> 00:31:36.100
