for basically spot intelligence,

00:32:54.940 --> 00:32:57.190
what was going to be useful
for the actual fighting

00:32:57.190 --> 00:32:59.650
that was going on at
that time in Korea.

00:32:59.650 --> 00:33:05.820
And after that, they were
shipped by ship from Yokohama

00:33:05.820 --> 00:33:08.190
