One is 73 conversation between
Kim Il-sung and [inaudible].

01:20:23.490 --> 01:20:30.650
In 1977, East German
cable on the relationship

01:20:30.650 --> 01:20:34.560
and 1986 between--
conversation between Kim Il-sung

01:20:34.560 --> 01:20:36.020
and a Mongolian official.

01:20:36.020 --> 01:20:40.260
The conversation with
[inaudible] is 13 pages.

01:20:40.260 --> 01:20:43.580
