01:24:58.840 --> 01:25:00.140
years old.

01:25:00.140 --> 01:25:03.550
So unless the policymaker
is really keen on history,

01:25:03.550 --> 01:25:07.960
which they probably should
be, but they're not obviously,

01:25:07.960 --> 01:25:11.040
you know, and I think our
collections are probably not

01:25:11.040 --> 01:25:12.340
